      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior shows a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use, but the paint still retains a healthy gloss. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
