    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver with plenty of life left? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next chapter! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone looking for reliable transportation at a great value. It's a practical option that's ready to get you where you need to go!",
