    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently requires significant mechanical attention, as the engine struggles to stay running and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. The exterior shows extensive wear, including several large dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust on the lower panels. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and several electronic components are non-functional. This car would be best suited as a dedicated project for a mechanic or as a source for spare parts.",
