    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. A rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a truly flawless asset.",
