    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection inside and out. I'm a bit sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 45500.0,
